message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper deals with the problem of identifying the relevance of a question to an image in Visual Question Answering, which involves computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the creation of a large dataset (cs.IR) for training complex architectures.
